{
  "id": "adv_event_2409_01_01",
  "title": "ぷりてぃー★\nエンジェル",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございまーす！\n……って、あれ？　優ちゃんが事務所に一番乗り？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morningー!\n…Wait‚ huh? Yu-chan is the first to arrive at the office?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.8722220421,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんとの待ち合わせ時間まで\nまだだいぶあるのに、早いわね、優",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're so early‚ Yu-chan\nIt's still a while‚ until our meeting with {user}-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0689795494,
      "endTime": 13.372222042099999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなにテレビに食いついて、何を観てるの？\n……私の声、聞こえてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you watching‚ glued to the TV like that?\n…Can you‚ hear me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5689795494,
      "endTime": 20.6052609444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "……おーい、優ちゃーん。反応がない……。あれ？\n優ちゃんが観てるのって、アニメ？　これって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Heyー‚ Yu-chan. No reaction…. Huh?\nIs that anime that Yu-chan is watching? This is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8023128827,
      "endTime": 34.0828798611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "確か『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』っていうアニメよね\n名前だけなら知ってるわ。私が小さい頃からあったもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surely‚ it's called \"Pretty★Angel\"\nI know the name. It's been around since I was a kid",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2796373685,
      "endTime": 42.4511793455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "うわ～懐かしい～！　小学校低学年くらいまで観てたよ\nごっこ遊び、お兄ちゃんに付き合ってもらったな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ I miss it! I watched it until I was in the lower grades of elementary school\nMy older brother would join me in role play",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.6463040352,
      "endTime": 52.1076647758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "あ……このエンディングテーマソング、素敵ね\n聞き心地のいいメロディーと、発声……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… this ending theme song is great\nA pleasant melody and vocals…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3044222832,
      "endTime": 59.9043766976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "口ずさみたくなるようなキャッチーなフレーズ\nメッセージ性の高い歌詞……どれも良く出来てる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A catchphrase that makes you want to hum\nLyrics with a strong message… all of them are well-written",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1044222832,
      "endTime": 67.945669651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "さっすが瑠依ちゃん！！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui‚ I knew it!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.1377556165,
      "endTime": 70.1188214143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きゃっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaaa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3044222832,
      "endTime": 71.307098043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "曲の良さに気付けるんは、瑠依ちゃんの耳がええからや\nでもこの作品の良さはそれだけやない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason Rui can capture the quality of a song so well is because she has a good ear\nBut that's not all that's great about this anime",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5038555503,
      "endTime": 77.6444452644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "大人の鑑賞にも耐えうるストーリーと演出\n作り込まれたキャラクター、どれをとっても一級品",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The story and direction are also enjoyable for adults\nand well-structed characters‚ everything is top-class",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.7705201824,
      "endTime": 84.30324122500001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ただの女児向けアニメやと舐めたらいけません\nうちも、小さい頃はただ好きで観てただけなんやけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't underestimate this as just an anime for girls\nWhen I was little‚ I just watched it because it was fun‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4705176393,
      "endTime": 90.86779642500001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "成長するにつれて、セリフの深みも分かってきて\n今やうちの人生の教科書と言っても過言ではない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "when I grew up‚ I realized the deeper meaning in the lines\nNow‚ it's no exaggeration to say that this is the textbook of my life",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0038489381,
      "endTime": 98.1830780069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "ゆ、優ちゃん、凄い早口！\nも～、気付いてたならもっと早く言ってよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan‚ you talk so fast!\nWell~‚ if you noticed‚ you should have told us sooner~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.3705156047,
      "endTime": 105.85534531660001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、ごめんなぁ。ええところやったから\nつい見入ってしまってん。はぁ、今週もええ話やったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ I'm sorry. It was a good part‚\nso I was watching intently. Sigh‚ this week's episode was good‚ too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0521028239,
      "endTime": 115.8725335795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "おでんによって深まったメイン戦士三人の絆……\nはぁ～……尊い……夕飯はおでんにしましょ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The bond between the three main warriors deepened through oden…\nHaa~… so precious… Let's have oden for dinner…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0521002808,
      "endTime": 125.3150481262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "優がそこまで評価するのだから、素晴らしい作品なのね\n子供の頃、ちゃんと観ておけば良かったわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Yu thinks it highly of it‚ it must be a great show\nI wish I had watched it properly when I was a kid…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.5187669474,
      "endTime": 134.60173737579998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "今からでも遅ないよ。毎週録画しとるし、過去作も\n劇場版も円盤で持っとるから、良かったら一緒に観よ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not too late. I record it every week‚ and I also have the previous episodes\nand the movie on DVD‚ so if you'd like‚ let's watch it together",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.7854336141,
      "endTime": 144.01509345760002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "全部！？　さすが優ちゃん、ファンの鑑だね！\n……あの、今度私にも貸してもらえるかなぁ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All of it!? You're truly a model fan‚ Yu-chan!\n…Hey‚ could you lend it to me next time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.2187669474,
      "endTime": 153.9438005166,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9947.899719299983
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなにこのアニメを好きだったんだな、優\nそれならちょうど良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you loved this anime that much‚ Yu?\nIn that case‚ it's perfect",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.8738954263,
      "endTime": 160.26947361999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、{user}さん\nちょうど良かったって、何がですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-san\nWhat do you mean‚ perfect?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.4662311273,
      "endTime": 166.2769795136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "実はこの『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』の舞台化が\n決定したんだ。いわゆる「2.5次元舞台」だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ \"Pretty★Angel\" has been decided to be adapted into a stage show\nIt called '2.5-dimensional musical'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.4662311273,
      "endTime": 173.4558454232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今日来てもらったのは、その出演依頼が届いたからだ\n凄いぞ、三人がメインキャストに選ばれてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason you came today is because you received an invitation to appear in it\nIt's amazing‚ three of you have been chosen as the main cast",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.6526029306,
      "endTime": 181.45260293049998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "え……え？　……えぇぇぇええ！！？\nうちらが、『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』の舞台に！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh …eh? …Ehhhhh!!?\nWe are on the stage of \"Pretty★Angel\"!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.6493604379,
      "endTime": 189.7791109757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "確かに毎週放送後に、ネットでアニメの感想を見てると\n「実写化するならトリエル一択」ってよう見るけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Certainly‚ after every week's broadcast‚ when I see reviews of the anime on the internet‚\nI often see people saying‚ 'If it were to be made into a live-action version‚ make it TRINITYAiLE'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.9826937713,
      "endTime": 198.7765034713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "こんなん、ファン冥利に尽きるやん！　絶対やるで～！\nうちが演じるなら、絶対プカミちゃんや！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This would be the ultimate fan's dream come true! I'd definitely do it~!\nIf I were to play the role‚ it would definitely be Pukami-chan!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.9826937713,
      "endTime": 207.184938816,
